</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_404</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">亲，你迷路了！</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>自定义分类notice的归档页面标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_tax</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'notice\'</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php setTitle</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>简单的代码分析</h2>\r\n<div id=\"sc_notice\">\r\n\r\n&lt;?php if ( is_home() ) { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n判断语句，例如这段代码就是判断是否为主页，其他页面代码类似，具体信息可以查看上面的代码。\r\n\r\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n博客主标题\r\n\r\n&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n连接符，读取主题设置页面中的连接符设置。\r\n\r\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'description\'); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n博客副标题\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n知道了一些简单的代码后，相信修改起来就容易多了吧！修改时一定要做好备份，如果在本地修改再上传的话，不要使用记事本修改，一定要使用专业的文本编辑工具，比如notepad++或editplus\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',	'如何自定义修改wordpress nana主题的网页标题样式',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2019-10-11 15:57:32',	'2019-10-11 07:57:32',	'',	49,	'http://wp.my/archives/2019/50',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(51,	1,	'2019-10-11 16:50:47',	'2019-10-11 08:50:47',	'<div class=\"single-content\">\n\n本站使用的是懿古今的nana主题wordpress版，在日常和站长的交流当中，发现很多站长对代码可以说是一无所知，已经有两个站长在群中询问关于nana主题如何自定义修改标题的问题，今天本来也不知道该写什么文章，正好就这个问题把nana主题的标题代码分析一下。\n\n要修改网页的标题，我们第一时间想到的就是head.php，但是打开head.php并没有发现关于标题&lt;title&gt;的代码，所以可以确定nana主题的标题代码没有直接写在head.php中，通过head.php中的代码，发现nana主题是调用了一个seo.php这个文件来编写关于标题的代码，通过下面的代码可以找到，这个文件的路径inc/functions/seo.php，想要修改标题代码就要用到这个文件。\n<pre class=\"lang:php decode:true \">&lt;?php get_template_part( \'inc/functions/seo\' ); ?&gt;</pre>\n找到要修改的文件，我们还要了解一下nana主题标题代码都用到了哪些代码，通过下面的代码可以根据对应分类来修改相应的标题。\n<h2>主页标题代码：</h2>\n<pre class=\"wrap:true lang:default decode:true\">&lt;?php if ( is_home() ) { ?&gt;&lt;title&gt;&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;&lt;?php bloginfo(\'description\'); ?&gt;&lt;?php if (get_query_var(\'paged\')) { echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\'));echo \'第\'; echo get_query_var(\'paged\'); echo \'页\';}?&gt;&lt;/title&gt;&lt;?php } ?&gt;</pre>\n<code lang=\"php\"><!--?php get_template_part( \'inc/functions/seo\' ); ?--></code>\n<h2>搜索结果标题</h2>\n<pre class=\"lang:php decode:true\">&lt;?php if ( is_search() ) { ?&gt;&lt;title&gt;搜索结果&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;&lt;/title&gt;&lt;?php } ?&gt;</pre>\n<h2>文章标题</h2>\n<pre class=\"lang:php decode:true\">&lt;?php if ( is_single() ) { ?&gt;&lt;title&gt;&lt;?php echo trim(wp_title(\'\',0)); ?&gt;&lt;?php if (get_query_var(\'page\')) { echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\'));echo \'第\'; echo get_query_var(\'page\'); echo \'页\';}?&gt;&lt;?php if(get_option(\'ygj_titlecat\')){echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\'));foreach((get_the_category()) as $category){echo $category-&gt;cat_name;}}?&gt;&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;&lt;/title&gt;&lt;?php } ?&gt;</pre>\n<h2>页面标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_page</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo trim</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">wp_title</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'\'</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"lit\">0</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>分类目录标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_category</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'cat\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'cat-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L3\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'cat-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L4\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">else</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L5\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php single_cat_title</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L6\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php endif</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">}?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>标签页面标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_tag</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'tag_id\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'tag-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L3\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'tag-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L4\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">else</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L5\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php single_tag_title</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\"\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">true</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L6\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php endif</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">}?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>文章归档标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_year</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'Y年\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_month</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'F\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">份所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_day</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'Y年n月j日\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>404页面标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_404</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">亲，你迷路了！</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>自定义分类notice的归档页面标题</h2>\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_tax</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'notice\'</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php setTitle</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>简单的代码分析</h2>\n<div id=\"sc_notice\">\n\n&lt;?php if ( is_home() ) { ?&gt;\n\n判断语句，例如这段代码就是判断是否为主页，其他页面代码类似，具体信息可以查看上面的代码。\n\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;\n\n博客主标题\n\n&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;\n\n连接符，读取主题设置页面中的连接符设置。\n\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'description\'); ?&gt;\n\n博客副标题\n\n</div>\n知道了一些简单的代码后，相信修改起来就容易多了吧！修改时一定要做好备份，如果在本地修改再上传的话，不要使用记事本修改，一定要使用专业的文本编辑工具，比如notepad++或editplus\n\n</div>\n<!--more-->',	'如何自定义修改wordpress nana主题的网页标题样式',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2019-10-11 16:50:47',	'2019-10-11 08:50:47',	'',	49,	'http://wp.my/archives/2019/51',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(76,	1,	'2019-10-11 17:04:33',	'2019-10-11 09:04:33',	'作为blog 里面肯定有“粘贴源代码”的情况，就需要源代码高亮显示，那还怎么看！经过本比对之后，<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/crayon-syntax-highlighter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Crayon Syntax Highlighter</a> 可能是最流行，功能最强大的一款代码高亮插件了。\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff5a54; font-weight: bold;\">注意：Crayon Syntax Highlighter 只支持php7.19*以下的版本，对于wp版本的实验室5.23仍然没有问题，但是刚开始php环境是7.3x，这个插件就不能显示正常了。</span>\r\n\r\n另外设置：我的推荐是：\r\n\r\n1）字体大小14，行高30；\r\n2）默认显示行编号；\r\n3）工具栏显示方式：从不显示；\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ps.w.org/crayon-syntax-highlighter/assets/banner-772x250.jpg\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://ps.w.org/crayon-syntax-highlighter/assets/banner-772x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"248\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>一、安装 Crayon Syntax Highlighter</strong>\r\n\r\n在 wordpress 管理后台，通过 插件，输入 Crayon Syntax Highlighter，点击安装就可以了。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/install_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-42 size-full\" src=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/install_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1356\" height=\"325\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>二、设置 Crayon Syntax Highlighter 样式</strong>\r\n\r\n安装完毕之后，对代码高亮的样式进行设置\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/setting_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-45 size-full\" src=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/setting_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"911\" height=\"99\" /></a>\r\n\r\n根据你的喜好设置，例如我们可以把代码样式设置成 Sublime Text 风格\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/setup_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-47 size-full\" src=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/setup_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"825\" height=\"727\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>三、使用 Crayon Syntax Highlighter 插入代码</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/use_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-62 size-full\" src=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/use_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1023\" height=\"124\" /></a>\r\n\r\n在弹出的输入框中 输入/插入 代码\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/add_code_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" data-lb-type=\"grouped-post\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-63 size-full\" src=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/add_code_Crayon_Syntax_Highlighter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"693\" height=\"639\" /></a>\r\n\r\n【原文链接】<a href=\"http://www.ipaomi.com/2017/08/01/wordpress-%e6%ba%90%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%81-%e9%ab%98%e4%ba%ae%e6%98%be%e7%a4%ba-crayon-syntax-highlighter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.ipaomi.com/2017/08/01/wordpress-源代码-高亮显示-crayon-syntax-highlighter/</a>',	'wordpress 源代码 高亮显示 (Crayon Syntax Highlighter)',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'73-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2019-10-11 17:04:33',	'2019-10-11 09:04:33',	'',	73,	'http://wp.my/archives/2019/76',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(53,	1,	'2019-10-11 15:59:18',	'2019-10-11 07:59:18',	'<header class=\"entry-header\">本站使用的是懿古今的<a title=\"【查看含有[nana]标签的文章】\" href=\"https://www.jiaoyawz.com/tag/nana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">nana</a>主题<a title=\"【查看含有[wordpress]标签的文章】\" href=\"https://www.jiaoyawz.com/tag/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wordpress</a>版，在日常和站长的交流当中，发现很多站长对代码可以说是一无所知，已经有两个站长在群中询问关于nana主题如何自定义修改标题的问题，今天本来也不知道该写什么文章，正好就这个问题把nana主题的标题代码分析一下。</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"single-content\">\r\n\r\n要修改网页的标题，我们第一时间想到的就是head.php，但是打开head.php并没有发现关于标题&lt;title&gt;的代码，所以可以确定nana主题的标题代码没有直接写在head.php中，通过head.php中的代码，发现nana主题是调用了一个seo.php这个文件来编写关于标题的代码，通过下面的代码可以找到，这个文件的路径inc/functions/seo.php，想要修改标题代码就要用到这个文件。\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php get_template_part</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'inc/functions/seo\'</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n找到要修改的文件，我们还要了解一下nana主题标题代码都用到了哪些代码，通过下面的代码可以根据对应分类来修改相应的标题。\r\n<h2>主页标题代码：</h2>\r\n您需要选择一个短代码\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_home</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'description\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>搜索结果标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_search</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">搜索结果</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>文章标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_single</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo trim</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">wp_title</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'\'</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"lit\">0</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'page\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'page\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_titlecat\'</span><span class=\"pun\">)){</span><span class=\"pln\">echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"kwd\">foreach</span><span class=\"pun\">((</span><span class=\"pln\">get_the_category</span><span class=\"pun\">())</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">as</span><span class=\"pln\"> $category</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span><span class=\"pln\">echo $category</span><span class=\"pun\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">cat_name</span><span class=\"pun\">;}}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>页面标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_page</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo trim</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">wp_title</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'\'</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"lit\">0</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>分类目录标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_category</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'cat\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'cat-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L3\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'cat-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$cat_ID </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L4\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">else</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L5\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php single_cat_title</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L6\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php endif</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">}?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>标签页面标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_tag</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'tag_id\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'tag-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L3\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'tag-title-\'</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">$term_id </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L4\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">else</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L5\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php single_tag_title</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\"\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">true</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">))</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\">echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'第\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo get_query_var</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'paged\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> echo </span><span class=\"str\">\'页\'</span><span class=\"pun\">;}?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L6\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php endif</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">}?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>文章归档标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_year</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'Y年\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L1\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_month</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'F\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">份所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"L2\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_day</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php the_time</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'Y年n月j日\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">所有文章</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>404页面标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_404</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">亲，你迷路了！</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>自定义分类notice的归档页面标题</h2>\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_tax</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'notice\'</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php setTitle</span><span class=\"pun\">();</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php echo stripslashes</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">get_option</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'ygj_lianjiefu\'</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php bloginfo</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"str\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/title&gt;</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>简单的代码分析</h2>\r\n<div id=\"sc_notice\">\r\n\r\n&lt;?php if ( is_home() ) { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n判断语句，例如这段代码就是判断是否为主页，其他页面代码类似，具体信息可以查看上面的代码。\r\n\r\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'name\'); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n博客主标题\r\n\r\n&lt;?php echo stripslashes(get_option(\'ygj_lianjiefu\')); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n连接符，读取主题设置页面中的连接符设置。\r\n\r\n&lt;?php bloginfo(\'description\'); ?&gt;\r\n\r\n博客副标题\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n知道了一些简单的代码后，相信修改起来就容易多了吧！修改时一定要做好备份，如果在本地修改再上传的话，不要使用记事本修改，一定要使用专业的文本编辑工具，比如notepad++或editplus\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',	'如何自定义修改wordpress nana主题的网页标题样式',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'49-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2019-10-11 15:59:18',	'2019-10-11 07:59:18',	'',	49,	'http://wp.my/archives/2019/53',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(52,	1,	'2019-10-11 15:58:43',	'2019-10-11 07:58:43',	'<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"single_info\"><span class=\"xiaoshi\"><span class=\"leixing\"><span class=\"yclx\">原创</span> </span></span><span class=\"date\">2019-04-25 21:44 </span> <span class=\"views\">阅读 148 次 </span><span class=\"comment\"><a href=\"https://www.jiaoyawz.com/2182.html#comments\">评论 2 条</a></span></div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"single-content\">\r\n\r\n本站使用的是懿古今的<a title=\"【查看含有[nana]标签的文章】\" href=\"https://www.jiaoyawz.com/tag/nana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">nana</a>主题<a title=\"【查看含有[wordpress]标签的文章】\" href=\"https://www.jiaoyawz.com/tag/wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wordpress</a>版，在日常和站长的交流当中，发现很多站长对代码可以说是一无所知，已经有两个站长在群中询问关于nana主题如何自定义修改标题的问题，今天本来也不知道该写什么文章，正好就这个问题把nana主题的标题代码分析一下。\r\n\r\n要修改网页的标题，我们第一时间想到的就是head.php，但是打开head.php并没有发现关于标题&lt;title&gt;的代码，所以可以确定nana主题的标题代码没有直接写在head.php中，通过head.php中的代码，发现nana主题是调用了一个seo.php这个文件来编写关于标题的代码，通过下面的代码可以找到，这个文件的路径inc/functions/seo.php，想要修改标题代码就要用到这个文件。\r\n<ol class=\"linenums\">\r\n 	<li class=\"L0\"><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php get_template_part</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\'inc/functions/seo\'</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">);</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n找到要修改的文件，我们还要了解一下nana主题标题代码都用到了哪些代码，通过下面的代码可以根据对应分类来修改相应的标题。\r\n<h2>主页标题代码：</h2>\r\n您需要选择一个短代码\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"pun\">&lt;?</span><span class=\"pln\">php </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\"> is_home</span><span class=\"pun\">()</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">?&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;title&gt;</span><span 